搞，导致软路由内置的防火墙形同虚设，攻击面大大增加。</p>\n<p>下午师傅上门要改回来了，现在后悔还来得及，问问大家桥接的必要性在哪里？没啥必要就直接改回来，还能省一个无线 AP</p>\n", "last_modified": 1670901989, "replies": 89, "id": 902139}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 194454, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 3651, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 585583, "username": "arvin01", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/arvin01", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/57ef171d5d88f1e0a087f557bcfddc7d?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/57ef171d5d88f1e0a087f557bcfddc7d?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/57ef171d5d88f1e0a087f557bcfddc7d?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1655879721, "last_modified": 1655879721}, "last_reply_by": "GeruzoniAnsasu", "last_touched": 1670963602, "title": "如何看待《三体》里的黑暗森林法则？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/902223", "created": 1670918173, "deleted": 0, "content": "黑暗森林法则说的是——文明和文明之间，不可能有真正的沟通，不可能有真正的信任，一旦接触，往往都是立即消灭对方。", "content_rendered": "黑暗森林法则说的是——文明和文明之间，不可能有真正的沟通，不可能有真正的信任，一旦接触，往往都是立即消灭对方。", "last_modified": 1670918473, "replies": 84, "id": 902223}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1608969785", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1608969785", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 3690, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785", "stars": 998, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 382312, "username": "ggp1ot2", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/ggp1ot2", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/da2c/7a71/382312_mini.png?m=1655554833", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/da2c/7a71/382312_normal.png?m=1655554833", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/da2c/7a71/382312_large.png?m=1655554833", "created": 1549503424, "last_modified": 1655554833}, "last_reply_by": "ipcjs", "last_touched": 1670938530, "title": "一个哭笑不得的问题，如何从无症状变成确诊？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/902098", "created": 1670893827, "deleted": 0, "content": "年初购买了疫情险，确诊赔 1w 。\r\n\r\n虽然现在还是好好的，但是感觉这两个月难逃一劫了。\r\n\r\n刚刚又查询了保单和出险材料。\r\n\r\n保险上明确说明了只有是医院出具的材料，证明你是确诊而不是无症状才能赔付。\r\n\r\n也就是只提供核酸阳性记录不行，无症状也不行。\r\n\r\n所以我想提前咨询下：**如果真的某一天发现自己阳了，怎么样才能找到医院让他们将我标记为确诊？**\r\n\r\n正确姿势是什么，感觉现在医院人满为患了，根本不会管你。\r\n\r\n坐标上海。", "content_rendered": "<p>年初购买了疫情险，确诊赔 1w 。</p>\n<p>虽然现在还是好好的，但是感觉这两个月难逃一劫了。</p>\n<p>刚刚又查询了保单和出险材料。</p>\n<p>保险上明确说明了只有是医院出具的材料，证明你是确诊而不是无症状才能赔付。</p>\n<p>也就是只提供核酸阳性记录不行，无症状也不行。</p>\n<p>所以我想提前咨询下：<strong>如果真的某一天发现自己阳了，怎么样才能找到医院让他们将我标记为确诊？</strong></p>\n<p>正确姿势是什么，感觉现在医院人满为患了，根本不会管你。</p>\n<p>坐标上海。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1670893827, "replies": 78, "id": 902098}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 194454, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 3651, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 271495, "username": "chihu", "